org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.job

Class JobState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.task.CommonAttribute
      • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.job.Job
        • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.job.JobState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<JobState>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientJobState, JobStateImpl

    @PublicAPI
public abstract class JobState
extends Job
implements Comparable<JobState>
    This class contains all informations about the state of the job. It also provides methods and static fields to order the jobs if you hold them in a list. It references the list of task contains in the job.
    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 0.9
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
